<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Why Your Property Earns More</title>

  <!-- Geist Font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #8b5e2f;
      --border-color: #c9a26b;
      --highlight-bg: #FFF6DD;
      --season-bg: #7A542A;
      --season-card: #EFCE8D;
      --text-dark: #222;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Geist', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #f4f4f4;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    /* ðŸ”½ SCALED PAGE */
    .page {
      width: 491px;
      height: 694px;
      background: #fff;
      position: relative;
      padding: 44px 56px;
    }

    /* BORDER */
    .page::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 22px;
      left: 22px;
      right: 22px;
      bottom: 34px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* LOGO */
    .corner-logo {
      position: absolute;
      top: 38px;
      right: 38px;
      height: 32px;
    }

    /* HEADING */
    .heading {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    /* HIGHLIGHT */
    .highlight {
      background: var(--highlight-bg);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color);
      padding: 12px 14px;
      font-size: 9.5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    /* SECTION TITLES */
    .section-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* SEASON PRICING */
    .season-wrapper {
      background: var(--season-bg);
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .season-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .season-card {
      background: var(--season-card);
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .season-card .label {
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #7A542A;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .season-card .price {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #000;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      padding: 4px 0;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    }

    .season-card .accuracy {
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #7A542A;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* BENEFITS */
    .benefits {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px 20px;
    }

    .benefit h4 {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .benefit p {
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* SKYLINE */
    .skyline {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      opacity: 0.08;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 18px;
      left: 22px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="page">

  <img src="/images/svg_logo.svg" class="corner-logo" alt="Logo">

  <h1 class="heading">WHY YOUR PROPERTY EARNS MORE?</h1>

  <div class="highlight">
    Short-term rental properties demonstrate <strong>superior revenue performance</strong> by
    strategically capitalizing on seasonal demand fluctuations. Our data-driven approach optimizes
    pricing across peak, shoulder, and low seasons, ensuring <strong>maximum profitability</strong>
    while maintaining competitive occupancy rates throughout the calendar year.
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">Average Daily Rate (ADR) by Season</div>

  <div class="season-wrapper">
    <div class="season-grid">

      <div class="season-card">
        <div class="label">LOW SEASON</div>
        <div class="price">AED <%= lowSeasonPrice %></div>
        <div class="accuracy"><%= lowSeasonAccuracy %> Accuracy</div>
      </div>

      <div class="season-card">
        <div class="label">PEAK SEASON</div>
        <div class="price">AED <%= peakSeasonPrice %></div>
        <div class="accuracy"><%= peakSeasonAccuracy %> Accuracy</div>
      </div>

      <div class="season-card">
        <div class="label">SHOULDER SEASON</div>
        <div class="price">AED <%= shoulderSeasonPrice %></div>
        <div class="accuracy"><%= shoulderSeasonAccuracy %> Accuracy</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">Owner Benefits & Value Proposition</div>

  <div class="benefits">
    <div class="benefit">
      <h4>Dynamic Revenue Capture</h4>
      <p>Leverage premium pricing during high-demand periods to maximize returns.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit">
      <h4>Market Intelligence</h4>
      <p>Real-time adjustments based on competitive analysis and demand forecasting.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit">
      <h4>Transparent Analytics</h4>
      <p>Clear insights into performance drivers and revenue attribution.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit">
      <h4>Consistent Profitability</h4>
      <p>Stable cash flow across all seasonal cycles.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <img src="/images/illustration.png" class="skyline" alt="Skyline">

  <div class="footer">Confidential Â© Royal Holiday Homes</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
